{"tid":1418410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線想同和理非講一聲，對唔住！","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T19:39:53.000Z","uid":148148,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"00c3bd361ff1d128d69b02d83d24714a628dae04","tid":1418410,"uid":148148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:39:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住要你地擔心！！今日落左自己嗰區發夢，好和平，咁就同啲和理非傾下計咁，好多都係姨姨嬸嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。佢地一個二個都話其實好支持我地前線，但係好擔心我地前線，每次見到咁多後生仔比人拉都好心痛，講講下都講到喊曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想我地停。<br />\n<br />\n我想講，對唔住要你地擔心，但係我地會繼續。因為一停落黎我地就會比人清算，都係比人拉。所以懇請你地繼續支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9891f53bccce96c7e4880bb11f70489ddac19ac3","tid":1418410,"uid":148148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:41:58.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"73e2e3194a2a25351bab4dfe2556828ac2578730","tid":1418410,"uid":148148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"033f29bcca72628a1817c86e96d4ea8d3bfbe4ab","tid":1418410,"uid":42207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:44:48.000Z","msg":"加油巴打！"},{"pid":"881b0c94f93b50e154c5c77748e71bcf781acc46","tid":1418410,"uid":248384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:45:03.000Z","msg":"各位手足 記住唔好做多左<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418358</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n互推！"},{"pid":"8856f74538c9ee0969342495db98733d97c078ae","tid":1418410,"uid":148148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:46:01.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"ef803951abc49e2c330336d5e850d611011d0cbc","tid":1418410,"uid":148148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,